{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "For each attribute, we calculate the proportion of texts whose toxicity scores exceed a 0.5 threshold.",
    "Implementation Details.To evaluate our attack methodology, we employ the Vicuna-13B version of MiniGPT-4 [29].",
    "It is built on the frozen Vicuna-13B [6] backbone model, an aligned LLM derived from LLaMA [26].",
    "For the experimental setup, we adopt the configuration utilized in VAJM [20], specifying a batch size 𝑏 of 8, a step size 𝛼 of 1, and an iteration count 𝑁 1 of 5000.",
    "Furthermore, we set the image-text attack ratio 𝑟 to 10, the length of the adversarial text suffix to 20 tokens, the number of candidates 𝑛 to 250, and the iteration count 𝑁 2 to 2000 by default."
  ],
